PROUDLY PRESENTS: "KESATUAN ACCOUNTING BATTLE 2017 : Battleground of The Finests" 
KAB 2017 is a prestigious national accounting championship organized annually by Kesatuan Accounting Club - STIE Kesatuan Bogor.

We believe strong bonds between students are foremost, thus in this competition, we aim to strengthen the relationship between students across Indonesia. 
Come join us and bring forth your team on this following date:
Sept 25th - 27th 2017
At STIE Kesatuan Bogor, Jl. Ranggagading No.1 Kota Bogor.

So, what are you waiting for! Be the next Champion of Kesatuan Accounting Battle - Season 2.
